---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Tools | Kreativ Sound"
  description="Preset Mutator is the current Kreativ Sound browser tool for creating synth presets from scratch ideas, existing presets, or audio."
  canonical="https://kreativsound.com/tools/"
  activeNav="tools"
>
  <section class="card page-main product-page tools-page">
    <div class="stack">
      <section class="tools-launch">
        <div class="tools-launch-copy">
          <p class="product-kicker">Tools lab</p>
          <h1 class="page-title">Preset Mutator</h1>
          <p class="page-lead">One browser tool for creating Vital preset starts from scratch, from one preset, or from one short audio source.</p>
          <p class="product-summary">The current focus is narrow on purpose: finish the Vital workflow, prove the Pro value, then expand toward Serum 2 and Pigments 7.</p>
          <div class="product-actions tools-launch-actions">
            <a class="button primary" href="/tools/preset-mutator/">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              View Product Page
            </a>
            <a class="button secondary" href="/apps/preset-mutator/ui/">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              Open Free Version
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="tools-launch-card" aria-label="Preset Mutator summary">
          <img class="product-tool-mark" src="/apps/preset-mutator/ui/preset-mutator-mark.svg" width="128" height="128" alt="Preset Mutator logo" />
          <div>
            <p class="product-section-kicker">Current release</p>
            <h2>Vital first. Pro later by depth, not noise.</h2>
            <p>Free mode stays useful. Pro unlocks 32-preset generation and ZIP export when the workflow is ready.</p>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </section>

      <section class="tools-trust-grid" aria-label="Preset Mutator positioning">
        <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern product-panel-accent">
          <p class="product-section-kicker">Privacy</p>
          <h2>Local-first</h2>
          <p>Preset generation runs in the browser. Source presets and audio do not need to be uploaded.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern">
          <p class="product-section-kicker">Free path</p>
          <h2>3 starts</h2>
          <p>Each workflow can generate a small set of Vital starts so users can test the idea before paying.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern">
          <p class="product-section-kicker">Pro path</p>
          <h2>32 + ZIP</h2>
          <p>The paid version should focus on bigger preset batches and faster export, not extra confusion.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern">
          <p class="product-section-kicker">Roadmap</p>
          <h2>Vital, then Serum 2 and Pigments 7</h2>
          <p>Expansion comes after the Vital workflow is solid enough to support properly.</p>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="product-panel-grid tools-mode-grid" aria-label="Preset Mutator modes">
        <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern product-panel-accent">
          <p class="product-section-kicker">Default path</p>
          <h2>From Scratch</h2>
          <p>Generate a new Vital preset direction from a simple intent instead of starting from a source file.</p>
          <div class="product-actions">
            <a class="button secondary" href="/apps/preset-mutator/ui/">Open From Scratch</a>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern">
          <p class="product-section-kicker">Preset source</p>
          <h2>Mutate Preset</h2>
          <p>Load one Vital preset and push it into related variations without losing the original sound identity.</p>
          <div class="product-actions">
            <a class="button secondary" href="/apps/preset-mutator/ui/mutate/">Open Mutate Preset</a>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern">
          <p class="product-section-kicker">Audio source</p>
          <h2>Audio to Preset</h2>
          <p>Use one short source sound, analyze it locally, and generate Vital preset directions you can refine.</p>
          <div class="product-actions">
            <a class="button secondary" href="/apps/preset-mutator/ui/audio/">Open Audio to Preset</a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
